name: Dividing Space
body:
### Spaces, Places, People.
My name is Lyzi. I'm a geographer / cartographer / amateur programmer / would-be statistician / writer / GIS technician / college football fan / human being. These are some things I'm making.

This is a work in progress. More things to come soon.
